On Linux:

Compile MCsquare with the command: make
(this should generate the executable MCsquare_linux)

Configure the simulation in config.txt
Then, run MCsquare with the launcher: ./MCsquare


On Windows:

Compile MCsquare using Makefile.mak

Configure the simulation in config.txt
Then, run MCsquare with the launcher: MCsquare.bat
